Yanzu da kasar Sin ta fara amfani da fasahar kere kere, Amurka za ta ninka yawan kudaden da take kashewa wajen binciken fasahar kere kere, in ji mai kirkirar fasahar kere kere Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a kamfanonin Google, Microsoft da Apple.
An yi wannan gargaɗin ne bayan da sassan gwamnatin Amirka suka sanar da cewa suna amfani da makaman da ake kira AI, ko da yake a hukumance, ba a kafa wani shiri na musamman game da makaman ba.
A shekarar da ta gabata, kasar Sin ta sanar da shirinta na zama shugaban duniya a fannin kirkirar kere-kere ta zamani nan da shekara 2030.
"Wannan zai zama kyakkyawan farawa don ninka adadin da ake kashewa a kan binciken AI, ganin cewa duk sauran ƙasashe sun fi Amurka baya, kuma muna jiran ganin babban ci gaba na gaba a fannin AI", in ji Lee.
"Raba da kudaden da ake kashewa zai iya ninka damar da ake da ita na samun ci gaba a fannin fasahar kere kere a Amurka", in ji Lee a hirarsa da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, marubucin littafin AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order wanda aka buga a wannan watan daga mai bugawa Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne shugaban kamfanin Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a Face++, daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin kere kere na kasar Sin.
Ya yi aiki a fannin ilimin kere kere a jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a shekarun 1980s, ya lashe kyautar 'American actor of the Year' a Othello, daga baya ya zama babban jami'in gudanarwa a Microsoft Research, kuma shugaban sashen harsunan Sin a Google.
Lee ya yi magana game da gasar fasaha ta baya, wadda gwamnatin Amurka ta gudanar, kamar gasar injiniyoyi ta Defence Department, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a gudanar da gasar ta gaba, don gano masu kirkiro na gaba.
Lee ya ce, sau da yawa, 'yan kimiyya a Amirka suna bukatar su yi aiki tuƙuru don su sami tallafi daga gwamnati.
"Ba kasar Sin ce ke karbar manyan ra'ayoyi ba, amma kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun dauki kwararrun mutane daga jami'o'i don yin aiki a kan ilimin Artificial Intelligence a shekarun baya.
Lee ya ce sauye-sauyen manufofin shige da fice na iya taimaka wa Amurka ta inganta binciken ilimin kere kere.
"Ina ganin ya kamata wadanda ke da digiri na biyu a fannin ilimin kere-kere na zamani su samu izinin zama a kasar nan", in ji shi.
