Cutar HIV: China ta ba da rahoton ƙaruwar masu kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14 cikin ɗari
Kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton karuwar mutane da suka kamu da cutar HIV ko kuma wadanda suka kamu da cutar a kasar da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya sun ce fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a ƙasar.
Kusan 40,000 sabbin cututtuka aka bayar da rahoton a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka ana samunsu ne ta wurin yin jima'i, kuma wannan ya bambanta da yadda ake samunsu a dā.
A dā, cutar kanjamau ta yaɗu sosai a wasu ɓangarorin ƙasar Sin domin ba da jini da aka yi wa ƙwayoyin cuta.
Amma, adadin mutanen da suke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji ma'aikatan lafiya na ƙasar Sin da suka yi magana a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, adadin mutanen da suke da kwayar cutar HIV ko kuma cutar AIDS ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000 a kowace shekara.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a tsakanin jama'ar LGBT na kasar Sin.
A shekarar 1997, an haramta luwadi a China, amma har yanzu ana nuna bambanci ga 'yan luwadi.
