Elizabeth Warren za ta yi tunanin yin takarar shugaban kasa a 2020
A ranar Asabar, Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta bayyana cewa tana da matukar sha'awar yin takarar shugabancin kasa bayan zaben da aka yi a watan da ya gabata.
Warren ta tabbatar da cewa za ta yi tunanin yin takara a wani taron jama'a a Holyoke, Massachusetts.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su yi wa gwamnatinmu gyare-gyare, kuma za mu bukaci mace ta yi shugabanci", in ji ta a wani rahoto da The Hill ta wallafa.
"Bayan 6 ga Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari da yin takarar shugabancin ƙasar".
Warren ya yi magana game da Shugaba Donald Trump a taron kuma ya ce yana jagorantar kasar a kan hanya mara kyau.
"Ina matukar damuwa game da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyya", in ji ta.
Warren ya kasance mai tsauraran ra'ayi game da Trump da kuma Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a matsayin babban mai shari'a.
A ranar Juma'a, Warren ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa "hakika dole ne mu sa FBI ta yi bincike kafin a gudanar da zaben.
Sai dai wani rahoto da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin masu jefa kuri'a a jihar Warren ba su amince ta tsaya takara a zaben 2020 ba.
Kashi hamsin da takwas cikin dari na masu son yin zabe a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata dan majalisar dattijan ya tsaya takara ba, a cewar wani binciken da Cibiyar Bincike kan Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk/Boston Globe ta wallafa.
Kashi 32 na masu sauraron sun ce sun amince da abin da ta ce.
Binciken ya nuna goyon baya mafi yawa ga takarar Deval Patrick, tsohon Gwamnan, inda kashi 38 suka ce suna goyon bayan takararsa, yayin da kashi 48 suka ce sun ki amincewa da takarar.
Wasu daga cikin 'yan takarar jam'iyyar Democrat da aka yi musu magana a kan zaben 2020 sun hada da Joe Biden, tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa, da Bernie Sanders, dan majalisar dattawa daga Vermont.
Biden ya ce zai yi sanarwa a watan Janairu, kamar yadda wani rahoto ya ruwaito daga kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press.
Sarah Palin ta yi magana game da harin da aka kai mata a kan hanyar da ta yi wa Donald Trump.
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya yi shekara guda a Iraqi bayan ya shiga soja a watan Satumba.
An kama shi kuma an tuhume shi da laifin tashin hankali na gida a daren Litinin
"'Ɗana yana fama da wahalar dawowa, ina tare da sauran iyalai da ke fama da raunin da yaƙin yaƙi ya yi da shi da kuma raunin da sojojinmu suka dawo da shi gida da shi,' in ji ta a gaban masu sauraro a wajen wani babban taron neman zaben Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta kira kama shi "giwa a cikin dakin" kuma ta ce ɗanta da sauran mayaƙan sun "koma gida kaɗan daban, sun kasance masu taurin zuciya, suna mamakin ko akwai girmamawa ga abin da abokan aikinsu a cikin sojoji da manyan sojoji da sauran sassan sojojin suka yi wa ƙasar. "
An kama shi a ranar Litinin a Wasilla, Alaska, ana tuhumarsa da aikata fyade a gida, da kuma kokarin hana a kawo rahoton aikata fyade a gida, da kuma aikata laifin shan giya a yayin da yake cikin maye, a cewar Dan Bennett, kakakin rundunar 'yan sanda ta Wasilla.
Jihohi 18 da Washington D.C. sun goyi bayan ƙalubalen sabuwar dokar 'yan gudun hijira
Jihohi 18 da kuma Washington, D.C. sun ba da doka don hana sabon tsarin da Amurka ta kafa na hana 'yan gudun hijira samun mafaka.
'Yan majalisa da wakilai daga jihohi 18 da birane da dama sun gabatar da takardun shaida a ranar Juma'a a Washington don tallafawa wani mai ba da shawara kan dokar, kamar yadda NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan wanda ya shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace v. Sessions ba, wadda kungiyar kare hakkin jama'a ta Amurka ta shigar a gaban kotun tarayya.
Ta ce mijinta da kuma 'ya'yansa maza masu aikata laifi sun yi mata fyade, amma jami'an gwamnatin Amurka sun ki amincewa da neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare ta a wani gidan kurkuku da ke Texas.
Masu shigar da ƙara da suka goyi bayan Grace sun ambata ƙasashen El Salvador da Honduras da kuma Guatemala a matsayin ƙasashen da suke da matsalar cin zarafi da kuma nuna ƙarfi a cikin gida, kuma waɗannan ƙasashen ne suka fi kawo yawan waɗanda suke neman mafaka a ƙasar Amirka.
Sabon tsarin ya soke dokar da Kwamitin da ke Kula da Daukar Daukar Buƙata na Ƙasashen Waje ya kafa a 2014 ta ba da damar ba da mafaka ga 'yan gudun hijira da ba su da takardar izini da suka gudu daga gidajensu.
A wata sanarwa da ya fitar a ranar Juma'a, babban lauyan gwamnatin tarayya, Karl Racine, ya ce wannan sabon matakin "ya yi watsi da dokoki da aka kafa shekaru da dama da suka gabata a jihohi da kuma ƙasashen duniya".
"Dokar tarayya ta bukaci a yanke hukunci kan duk wani neman mafaka bisa ga hujjoji da kuma yanayin da ake nema, kuma wannan ya sabawa wannan ka'ida", in ji rahoton kotun.
Masu gabatar da kara sun kara da cewa a cikin rahoton cewa dokar hana shigowar baƙi tana da lahani ga tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna mai da hankali ga cewa baƙi sun fi saurin kafa kamfanoni da kuma samar da mahimman ma'aikata.
A watan Yuni, Jeff Sessions, Babban Mai Shari'a ya umurci manyan lauyoyi da su daina ba da mafaka ga duk wanda aka yi wa dūka ko cin zarafin da ya shafi gida.
"Wadanda suka bar kasarsu saboda zalunci saboda launin fata, addini, kabilanci, ko kuma bangaren siyasa za su iya neman mafaka", in ji Sessions a sanarwar da ya fitar a ranar 11 ga Yuni.
Ba a taɓa yin amfani da maganin warkarwa don magance dukan matsaloli ba, har da matsaloli masu tsanani da mutane suke fuskanta a kowace rana a faɗin duniya.
