Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin amfani da labaran da ke nuna cewa tana da makami mai guba
Bayan mako guda da jaridar China ta wallafa wani talla mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka, inda aka yi ta yin magana game da fa'idodin kasuwanci tsakanin kasashen biyu, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da yin amfani da kafofin watsa labarai na Amurka don tallata tallace-tallace.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba game da wani talla da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta buga a cikin Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi yawan masu wallafa labarai a jihar Iowa, bayan da ta zargi China da cewa ta yi kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dattawa da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na son tsoma baki a zaben da aka yi a majalisar dokokin Amurka, ya janyo abin da wasu jami'an Amurka suka fada wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters, ya zama wani sabon mataki a wani yunkuri na Washington na matsa wa China lamba.
Ko da yake ba laifi ba ne gwamnatocin wasu ƙasashe su riƙa tallata kayayyakin da suke sayarwa don su ƙarfafa kasuwanci, amma har yanzu akwai ƙalubale tsakanin Beijing da Washington a kan batun cinikayya, kuma sun kafa takunkumi a kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su daga ƙasashen biyu.
Masana na China da Amurka sun ce kudaden da China ta yi amfani da su a farkon yakin cinikayya an yi su ne don cutar da 'yan ci-rani a jihohi kamar Iowa, wanda ya yi watsi da jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa na tsawon lokaci, wanda jiharsa ta fitar da kayan aikin gona da yawa zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
A cikin wata sanarwa da ya wallafa a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, Branstad ya ce "China ta ƙara tsananta mana ta hanyar wallafa wasu labaran ƙiyayya a jaridunmu masu zaman kansu".
"A fadada shirinsa na talla, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi amfani da 'yancin fadin albarkacin baki da Amurka take da kuma 'yan jarida masu 'yanci ta hanyar saka talla a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad a cikin labarinta.
"A wani bangare kuma, babu wata murya ta nuna rashin amincewa a kantunan sayar da jaridu da ke kan titunan birnin Beijing, kuma babu wani tabbacin nuna bambancin ra'ayin da Sinawa za su iya yi game da matsalar tattalin arzikin kasar Sin, inda kafofin watsa labarai ke daure a hannun Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya ce wata babbar jaridar kasar Sin ta ƙi buga labarinsa, amma bai bayyana ko wace jarida ba ce.
Masana sun yi gargadin cewa 'yan Republican na janye hankalin mata masu jefa kuri'a daga zaben shugaban kasa na shekara-shekara ta hanyar amfani da batun Kavanaugh.
Masana sun yi gargadin cewa za a samu mummunan sakamako, musamman daga mata, a zaben na tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, saboda yawan 'yan Republican da suka goyi bayan Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama alkalin kotun kolin kasar, wanda ya yi watsi da zargin da ake yi masa na cin zarafin mata.
Akwai babban motsin rai a kan wannan batu, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun bayyana a fili cewa suna so su fara jefa kuri'a.
"Ba za a iya yin wasa da wannan ba", in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse, a jaridar The Hill, a wata kasida da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana shakkar cewa kiran da ɗan majalisar dattijan Arizona Jeff Flake ya yi a minti na ƙarshe game da binciken da FBI ke yi zai sa masu jefa ƙuri'a su yi fushi.
"'Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru a jiya ba, ba za su manta da gobe ba, ba za su manta da Nuwamba ba,' in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar MoveOn, a ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda wata jaridar Washington D.C. ta ruwaito.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a masu zanga-zangar sun rera "November ne na gabatowa!" a lokacin da suke zanga-zangar a lokacin da 'yan Republican da ke da iko a kan kwamitin yanke hukunci suka yanke shawarar ci gaba da zaben Kavanaugh, duk da shaidar da Dr. Christine Blasey Ford ta bayar, a cewar Mic.
"Za a yi amfani da dukkan karfin da masu jefa kuri'a ke da shi da kuma zafin zuciyarsu", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wanda ba shi da wata alaka da siyasa, a shafinsa na kafar yada labarai.
"Mutane za su ce mun riga mun yi ƙwazo sosai, kuma hakan gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya zama mafi girma, musamman ma a tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a unguwannin karkara da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, wadanda ba su son shugaban kasa, amma ba sa yawan jefa kuri'a.
Masu sharhi sun yi hasashen cewa 'yan Republican za su yi hamayya idan aka yi kokarin tabbatar da Kavanaugh, har ma da shaidar Ford inda ta bayyana zarginsa na yin lalata da shi.
"Wannan babban rashi ne ga jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Still, tsohon memba na kwamitin jam'iyyar Republican, a farkon makon da ya gabata, kamar yadda NBC News ta ruwaito.
"Ba wai batun kuri'ar kwamitin ba ne ko kuma kuri'ar karshe ko kuma a bar Kavanaugh a kan kujera, wannan ma batun yadda 'yan Republican suka yi da kuma yadda suka yi da shi ne", Guy Cecil, shugaban kungiyar Priorities USA, ta ce a lokacin da yake jawabi a yayin da ake tattaunawa da 'yan jarida.
Amma, da alama, Amurkawa ba su da ra'ayin da ya dace game da wanda za a gaskata, bisa ga shaidar da Ford da Kavanaugh suka bayar, kuma mafi yawan jama'a sun goyi bayan na biyun.
Wani sabon binciken da aka gudanar da kamfanin YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun amince ko kuma sun yarda da kalaman da Ford ya yi, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun amince ko kuma sun yarda da kalaman da Kavanaugh ya yi.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun ce suna ganin Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a shaidarsa, amma kashi 30 ne kawai suka ce hakan game da Ford.
Bayan da Flake ya kira, FBI yanzu tana binciken zargin da Ford ya yi da kuma na aƙalla wata mata, Deboruh Ramirez, a cewar wani rahoto na Guardian.
A gaban kwamitin da'a na majalisar dattawa a makon da ya gabata, Ford ta ba da shaida a gaban kotu cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade a lokacin da take 'yar shekara 17.
Ramirez ta ce Kavanaugh ya yi lalata da ita a lokacin da suke liyafar biki a makarantar Yale a shekarun 1980s.
Wanda ya kirkiri intanet din yana da shirin kafa sabuwar intanet don yaki Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro intanet, yana shirin kafa kamfanin sadarwa don ya yi nasara da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikin karshe na wannan babbar fasahar, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ya gina kan Solid, wani aikin budewa da Berners-Lee ya yi.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanne mutane ke da izinin samun damar yin amfani da bayanan.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa'azi cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "tabbatawar sararin samaniya".
"Dole ne mu yi haka yanzu", in ji shi game da kamfanin mai shuka shuke-shuke.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasaha daga Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu kantin sayar da bayanai na kan layi ko POD.
Za ka iya samun jerin sunayen lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan da za ka yi, kalandarka, kundin waƙoƙin ka, da kuma wasu abubuwan da kake amfani da su a kanka da kuma a wurin aiki.
Wannan yana da kamar Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna cikin wani burauzar kuma duk suna aiki tare.
Abu na musamman game da wannan hanyar musayar bayanai ita ce, yana da gaba ɗaya a hannun mai amfani wanda zai iya samun damar yin amfani da shi.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "Samun Zaɓin Mutum ta Amfani da Bayanai".
A cewar John Bruce, shugaban kamfanin, manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da kayan aiki, tsari da kuma ilimin da ya dace don taimakawa wajen samar da Solid ga kowa.
A yau, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani kamfanin tsaro wanda IBM ta saya, wasu masu shirye-shirye waɗanda aka ɗauka a matsayin masu haɓaka don yin aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shirye masu sa kai.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu fasaha a duk duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen kai tsaye ta amfani da kayan aikin da aka bayar a shafin Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba za su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da ko za a fara sauyi na gaba daya wanda zai kawo canjin tsarin kasuwancin su na yanzu cikin dare daya.
Ba ma tambayar su.
A wani rubutu da aka wallafa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Inrupt yana da burin samar da makamashi a harkokin kasuwanci da kuma tsarin da zai taimaka wajen kare gaskiya da ingancin sabon shafin yanar gizon da aka gina a kan Solid.
A shekara ta 1994 Berners-Lee ya kawo sauyi a yanar gizo lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya zama sanannen mai magana a kan batun nuna wariya ta yanar gizo.
Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da zama wanda ya kafa kuma shugaban kungiyar yanar gizo ta duniya, Web Foundation of the Open Data Institute, har ma a lokacin da yake kafa Inrupt.
"Ina da kwarin guiwa game da sabuwar zamanin Intanet", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: Wani limami da aka ba shi lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya
Shi ne kawai firist ɗan Ingilishi da aka ba wa lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na ɗaya, wanda aka yi wa wani soja da ya yi yaƙi a garinsu shekaru 100 bayan haka.
Séra Bernard Vann, wanda ya kasance babban janar a cikin rundunar, ya sami wannan gicciye a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a harin da aka kai wa Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma, bayan kwana huɗu sai wani ɗan harbi ya kashe shi, kuma bai san cewa an ba shi lambar yabo mafi girma a rundunar sojojin Britaniya ba.
'Yan sanda biyu da suka gano shi sun bayyana wani abin tunawa da shi a wani wurin da aka yi wa ado a Rushden, Northamptonshire, ranar Asabar.
Ɗaya daga cikin 'ya'yan kakansa, Michael Vann, ya ce "yana da ban mamaki" cewa an kafa wannan abin tunawa daidai shekara 100 bayan mutuwar kakansa.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, jarumin Vann ya ja-goranci sojojinsa suka ƙetare Canal de Saint-Quentin a ƙarƙashin babban hazo da kuma harbin bindigogi.
Daga baya, ya yi tsere zuwa inda za a harbi sojoji, kuma da "gaba gaɗi mai-girma" ya ja-goranci sojojin zuwa gaba, kafin ya harbi sojoji uku da bindiga da aka ɗora a ƙasa da ya yi amfani da shi.
Wani mataimakin shugaban ya mutu a hannun 'yan bindiga a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, watanni kaɗan kafin a daina yaƙin.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72 ya ce, "Hakkin da kakan ya yi ya sa na kasance mai tawali'u, ba abin da zan taɓa yi ba".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa, Dr. James Vann, sun kuma ba da kyautar kyautar bayan bikin, wanda Brentwood Imperial Youth Band ya jagoranci.
Michael Vann ya ce ya ji daɗin kasancewa a cikin wannan wasan kwaikwayon, ya kuma kara da cewa "alamar gwarzo na gaskiya ta bayyana a cikin goyon bayan da mutane da yawa ke nunawa".
MMA magoya bayan sun kasance a farke dukan dare don kallon Bellator 206, maimakon haka, sun ga Gurru Gish
Ka yi tunanin, yin farkawa duk dare don ganin Bellator 206 cike da mutane, kawai don a hana ku kallon babban taron.
Wasannin sun kunshi 13 daga San Jose, 6 daga cikin wasannin sun kasance a cikin babban shirin kuma an nuna su kai tsaye a duk dare a Burtaniya a tashar Channel 5.
Da ƙarfe 6 na safe, sa'ad da Gegard Mousasi da Rory McDonald suke shirin yin faɗa, sai masu sauraron gidan rediyon a ƙasar Ingila suka yi mamaki sa'ad da aka canja daga wani shiri zuwa wani shiri mai suna Gurra Grass.
Wasu sun yi rashin farin ciki bayan sun yi barci don su kalli wasan.
Wani mai goyon baya a shafin Twitter ya bayyana sauya fasalin zuwa "yarinyar" a matsayin "wani irin barkwanci".
"A bisa ka'idar gwamnati, ba a shirya wannan fim ɗin don masu sauraro da ƙarfe shida na safe, don haka sai suka sauya shi zuwa fim na yara", in ji Dave Schwartz, mataimakin darektan tallace-tallace da sadarwa na kamfanin Bellator, lokacin da aka tambaye shi a cikin shirin.
Kwankwaso mai kyau, a'a.
Scott Coker, shugaban kamfanin Bellator ya ce za su sake duba jadawalinsu kuma su yi la'akari da masu sauraro a Burtaniya a nan gaba.
"Ina ganin idan na yi tunani game da wannan sake dubawa cewa za mu iya yiwuwa warware wannan",Coker ce.
Amma sa'a ta yi 6 a ranar Lahadi da safe a wurin, kuma ba za mu iya warware wannan matsalar ba sai ranar Lahadi a lokacinmu, wanda a wurin su ranar Laraba ce.
Amma muna aiki a kan wannan.
Ku yi imani da ni, a lokacin da aka canja saƙon, an aika da sakonnin rubutu da yawa, kuma ba dukan su ne masu kyau ba.
Muna ƙoƙarin gyara wannan, muna tunanin cewa wata matsala ce ta fasaha.
Amma ba haka ba ne, wannan matsala ce ta jama'a.
Zan iya yin alkawari cewa wannan ba zai faru ba a lokaci na gaba.
Mun rage yawan yaƙinmu zuwa biyar maimakon shida kamar yadda muka saba, amma mun yi ƙoƙari sosai kuma mun yi fice.
Wannan yanayi ne mai ban tausayi.
Tom Daley ya sami 'yanci saboda jima'i
Tom Daley, wani ɗan wasan tsalle-tsalle a gasar Olympics ya ce ya yi rashin jituwa da wasu a lokacin da yake girma saboda sha'awarsa na yin jima'i, amma hakan ya motsa shi ya yi nasara.
Daley, ɗan shekara 24 ya ce bai san cewa shi ba kamar sauran mutane ba har sai da ya je makarantar kimiyya.
A cikin shirin rediyo na Desert Island Discs na Radio 4 tare da Lauren Laverne, Daley ya ce yana magana ne game da haƙƙin 'yan luwadi don ba wasu yanci.
Ya kuma ce yin renon yara ya janye masa sha'awar lashe gasar Olympics.
