Dalilin da ya sa yakin kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya zama da amfani ga Beijing
An fara harbin bindiga a yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, kuma duk da cewa yaƙin ya yi nisa da ƙarewa, amma ƙwararrun masana sun ce cinikin da ke tsakanin Amurka da Sin zai iya amfanar Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci.
A farkon wannan shekarar, shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya zartar da takunkumin da ya shafi manyan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa daga kasar, kamar su, makamashi mai amfani da hasken rana, da karafa, da kuma ƙarfe.
Babban abin da ya faru a wannan makon shi ne sabon jadawalin da aka sanya wa kayayyakin da suka kai dala biliyan 200 da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
A kowane lokaci, Beijing tana amsawa da irin wannan kalaman, kuma a kwanan nan ta saka haraji mai yawa, wato kashi 5 zuwa 10 bisa ɗari a kan kayayyakin da Amurka ta shigo da su da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
A yau, kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin yin martani ga takunkumin da Amurka ta kafa, kuma ba za ta yi kasa a gwiwa ba nan ba da daɗewa ba.
Don samun Washington ta yi tsalle, dole ne a yi watsi da buƙata, amma zai zama abin kunya ga shugaban China Xi Jinping ya yi watsi da Amurka a fili.
Amma masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi daidai da wasannin, to matsin lamba daga yakin cinikayya da Amurka zai iya yin tasiri mai kyau a kan Sin a cikin dogon lokaci, ta hanyar rage bukatar da ake da shi na masu hada-hadar tattalin arziki ga juna.
"Gaskiyar cewa yanke shawara na siyasa na Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayin da zai haifar da koma bayan tattalin arziki a kowace ƙasa, ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu kallo suka yarda da shi", in ji Abigail Grace, mai bincike da ke mai da hankali kan Asiya a cibiyar New American Security.
Ministan Harkokin Waje na Syria ya ce 'ba za a sake dawo da 'yan gudun hijira ba'
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta karɓi 'yan gudun hijirar da za su koma ƙasarsu da yardar rai, kuma tana neman taimako don sake gina ƙasar da ke cikin mawuyacin hali bayan yaƙi da aka yi na tsawon shekaru bakwai.
Ministan harkokin wajen kasar, Walid al Moualem, ya yi jawabi a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, ya ce yanayin da ake ciki a kasar na kara samun sauki.
"YANZU, yanayin duniya ya fi kwanciyar hankali da kuma kwanciyar hankali, saboda nasarar da aka samu a yaƙi da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati ta ci gaba da kawo sauyi ta hanyar gina wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka yi wa katanga.
Yanzu, an shirya shirye-shiryen 'yan gudun hijira don komawa ƙasarsu da suka tilasta musu su bar saboda ta'addanci da kuma manufofin tattalin arziki na yau da kullum da suka saɓa wa rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma aikin su.
An kiyasta cewa sama da 'yan gudun hijira miliyan 5.5 ne suka bar kasarsu tun lokacin da aka fara yaƙin a shekara ta 2011.
Wasu miliyan shida da suka rage a ƙasar suna bukatar taimako.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Siriya za ta yi farin ciki idan aka taimaka mata wajen sake gina ƙasar.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba za su amince da taimakon da aka yi wa sharadi ba ko kuma taimakon da ƙasashen da ke kawo wa 'yan tawayen suka bayar ba.
Turai ta lashe Ryder Cup a Paris
Tawagar Turai ce ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 bayan da ta doke tawagar Amurka da ci 16.5 da maki 10.5 a filin wasan Le Golf National da ke wajen birnin Paris na kasar Faransa.
A yanzu, Amirka ta yi hasarar sau shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta ci gasar Ryder ba tun daga shekara ta 1993.
Ƙasar Turai ta sake samun nasara sa'ad da 'yan wasan ƙasar Denmark, da ɗan wasan ƙasarsu Thomas Bjorn ya ja-goranci suka sami maki 14.5 da ake bukata don su yi nasara a kan ƙasar Amirka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a mafi yawan gasar, ya buga kwallo a raga a rami na 16, wanda ya zama na 3, kuma ya rasa wasan da Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiya Molinari ya ci nasara a dukkan wasannin da ya buga, inda ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa 4 da suka ci nasara a gasar 5-0-0, tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya yi rashin nasara 5&4 a hannun Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark, amma ya kasance a matsayi na ƙarshe a cikin jerin 'yan wasan Turai.
Dan wasan da ya fi kowa a duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya yi rashin nasara da ci biyu da daya a hannun dan wasan Ingila Ian Poulter, wanda ya buga wasan da zai iya zama na karshe a gasar cin kofin Ryder Cup.
Sergio Garcia na Spain, wanda ya buga gasar Ryder sau takwas, ya zama dan wasan Turai mafi nasara a gasar da ya yi nasara sau 25.5.
"Ba na yawan yin kuka, amma yau ba zan iya dainawa ba.
Wannan shekara ta kasance mai wuya.
Ina godiya ga Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya amince da ni.
Ina farin ciki da na dawo da kofin.
Wannan game da tawagar ne, kuma na yi farin cikin taimakawa", in ji Garcia bayan nasarar Turai.
A ranar Lahadi, ya doke Tiger Woods, wanda shi ne gwarzon 'yan wasan golf a Amurka, sau biyu da daya.
"Na yi matukar alfahari da na doke Tiger Woods, na girma ina kallon shi", in ji Rahm mai shekara 23.
Woods ya yi rashin nasara a dukkan wasanninsa hudu a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da maki 13-21-3 a gasar Ryder Cup.
Wannan sakamako ne mai ban mamaki ga ɗaya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa a tarihi, wanda ya lashe manyan kofuna 14 kuma yana da matsayi na biyu kawai ga Jack Nicklaus.
A karshen mako, 'yan wasan Amurka sun sha fama da rashin samun kansu a filin wasa, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, wadanda suka yi ta yin kwallo a duk fafatawar.
Shugaban Amurka Jim Furyk, bayan da ya ji takaicin yadda tawagarsa ta yi, ya ce, "Ina alfahari da su, sun yi gwagwarmaya.
A wani lokaci da safe ne muka soma tura turawa zuwa Turai.
Mun rasa shi a kasa.
Na ɗauki Thomas.
Shi ne mai girma shugaban.
Dukan 'yan wasansa 12 suna wasa sosai.
Za mu sake haɗuwa, zan yi aiki tare da PGA ta Amirka da kuma Kwamitin Ryder na Ƙasar, kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina ƙaunar waɗannan mutane 12 kuma ina alfahari da kasancewa a matsayin mai kula da su.
Dole ne ku yi amfani da shi.
Sun fi mu wasa.
